{"type": "article", "id": 21351, "title": "工业感的地毯", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-27T07:30:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607111734D1aAP92Bz4QfJI3h.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是英国设计师 Tom Dixon 带来的地毯系列，他从伦敦的地铁轨道、泰晤士河的河水以及拼接砖块等元素出发，设计了烟雾、裂缝、冲刷等 7 种不同的图景。它们已经转化为线条、方块等抽象的图案，有种凝固的美，也隐隐透露出了工业感。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150920ctoZplieB5zXWawy.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1152\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.40831296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150921bFGPJMeAwr9QvgdC.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1091\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33374083\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150922Y7bmpT2OC6AvkDx8.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33374083\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150922FQvwXruIfDGc6nyM.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1191\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.45599022\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}